  <refnamediv>
    <refname>readc_</refname>
    <refpurpose> read a character string</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>[c]=readc_(unit)
[c]=readc_()</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para><literal>readc_</literal> reads a character string.
    This function allows one to interrupt an exec file without <literal>pause</literal>;
    the exec file stops until carriage return is made.</para>
  </refsection>
